Four-panel technical diagram showing advanced RAG techniques: 1) HyDE: User Query -> LLM generates Hypothetical Document -> Embed -> Search. 2) Multi-Query: Query -> LLM generates 3-5 variants -> Parallel Search -> Deduplicate -> Top-K. 3) Cross-Encoder Re-Ranker: Query+Doc pairs -> Joint Attention -> Relevance Scores -> Re-ranked Top-5. 4) CRAG: Retrieval -> Evaluator (LLM Judge) -> Score 1-5 -> Generate/Refuse/Web Search. Clean grid layout, arrows, minimal text.